  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/af19e3148a676ccf22340704c4acb783.avif?t=1700469062\" width=603 height=150 /></span><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue is a social thriller set in a tropical island resort: you’ve been kidnapped and forced to participate in a twisted reality TV show with 10 strangers. At the end of your stay, you’ll receive $500,000. There’s just one catch—on the island there are no rules, and no hope of rescue.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.poster.avif?t=1700469062\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.webm?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.mp4?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue’s story explores human nature and how far people will go for social clout, wealth, and their own desires—and how much further they might be willing to go when they have permission to ignore the rules.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.poster.avif?t=1700469062\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.webm?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.mp4?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/898c0b10aab67e01bee2d8e61ecbaa4b.avif?t=1700469062\" width=603 height=150 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple narrative paths<br></li><li>A provocative character-driven story<br></li><li>A diverse cast of characters with intriguing personalities and backstories<br></li><li>Hours of voice-acted dialogue<br></li><li>A full-length original soundtrack with music from Shinji Hosoe (<i>Zero Escape</i>), and Matias Lehtoranta</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/fefd1af8689cde20ac26b673898d6554.poster.avif?t=1700469062\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/fefd1af8689cde20ac26b673898d6554.webm?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/fefd1af8689cde20ac26b673898d6554.mp4?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/fcb2295e885b78433ad9b94b2ca51fb7.avif?t=1700469062\" width=603 height=150 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/af19e3148a676ccf22340704c4acb783.avif?t=1700469062\" width=603 height=150 /></span><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue is a social thriller set in a tropical island resort: you’ve been kidnapped and forced to participate in a twisted reality TV show with 10 strangers. At the end of your stay, you’ll receive $500,000. There’s just one catch—on the island there are no rules, and no hope of rescue.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.poster.avif?t=1700469062\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.webm?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/8230b64571c8853d549d43b76aba3c39.mp4?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inescapable: No Rules, No Rescue’s story explores human nature and how far people will go for social clout, wealth, and their own desires—and how much further they might be willing to go when they have permission to ignore the rules.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.poster.avif?t=1700469062\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.webm?t=1700469062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170520/extras/cd8e5585a85a3310f6a27df64eb5eb75.m